2025-09-30 11:31:59,594 - INFO - Strategy Summary: The analysis highlights that balancing aspirate and dispense speeds, along with adjusting wait times, can significantly influence deviation, variability, and time outcomes. The speed-focused strategy aims to reduce cycle times by optimizing for faster aspirate and dispense speeds with minimal wait times, while the accuracy-focused strategy leverages the observed minimal deviation configurations. The Pareto front exploration attempts to achieve a balanced trade-off between accuracy and efficiency, expanding into less explored parameter combinations.
